dservice-1,Running thread AdService--stress-17492370061,出现次数:1\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["adservice-2", "adservice-0", "adservice-1"], "service_name": ["adservice"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-08", "aiops-k8s-03", "aiops-k8s-07"]}, "matched_anomaly": "The system experienced an anomaly from 2025-06-06T19:10:06Z to 2025-06-06T19:33:06Z. Please infer the possible cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-06 19:10:06+00:00 to 2025-06-06 19:33:06+00:00"}, "log_data_collected": true, "trace_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"frontend->frontend\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"frontend->shippingservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"frontend->cartservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend调用自身的AdService/GetAds操作，延迟从正常平均5549.49ms增加到异常平均31949.90ms，延迟倍数约为5.76倍。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend调用productcatalogservice的GetProduct操作，延迟从正常平均8592.95ms增加到异常平均10456.76ms，延迟倍数约为1.22倍。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend调用shippingservice的GetQuote操作，延迟从正常平均208.08ms增加到异常平均507.68ms，延迟倍数约为2.44倍。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice调用shippingservice的ShipOrder操作，延迟从正常平均231.72ms增加到异常平均8307.50ms，延迟倍数约为35.85倍。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend调用cartservice的GetCart操作，延迟从正常平均25581.50ms增加到异常平均12167.16ms，延迟倍数约为0.48倍（可能为Fast Fail）。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice调用redis的HGET操作